{"tid":527671,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《名偵探比卡超》新作公佈 又識西面又識撩女仔","createTime":"2018-01-13T02:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T07:13:45.000Z","uid":72478,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"96111e40dfb43448163a94cacfbddf99298d7446","tid":527671,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T02:47:15.000Z","msg":"片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=d6Qg-8_7ngs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1%26v%3Dd6Qg-8_7ngs&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1af8b624\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=d6Qg-8_7ngs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/games/transform/w532h318/20180113/_yas-fyqrewh5209685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fgames%2Ftransform%2Fw532h318%2F20180113%2F_yas-fyqrewh5209685.jpg&h=0c359d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Pok&eacute;mon Company宣布，原先日本獨佔的3DS遊戲《名偵探柯南：新搭檔誕生》將登陸歐美等全球市場，而且是全新增強版新作，日本也將發行，還將附加「比卡超」的Amiibo玩具，官方公佈首部預告片，本作中的「比卡超」正如「Ted」一樣，非常好色，破案的同時還會瘋狂撩妹。(我唔知條片邊個位見到佢好咸濕)<br />\n<br />\n玩家將扮演男主角、精靈訓練師Tim Goodman，跟隨這隻會說話的名偵探「比卡超」一起追尋失蹤的父親，期間還將遇到女記者，即本作的女主角，她的小精靈是傻鴨，不過比卡超對這個女主竟然還有非分之想，可以說是十分滑稽了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/games/transform/w550h295/20180113/zcFL-fyqrewh5211128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fgames%2Ftransform%2Fw550h295%2F20180113%2FzcFL-fyqrewh5211128.jpg&h=6d1f120e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/games/transform/w550h229/20180113/RAug-fyqrewh5212630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fgames%2Ftransform%2Fw550h229%2F20180113%2FRAug-fyqrewh5212630.jpg&h=cd6dcad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/games/transform/w550h309/20180113/HKkD-fyqrewh5213878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fgames%2Ftransform%2Fw550h309%2F20180113%2FHKkD-fyqrewh5213878.jpg&h=2dcd3501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，官方還將為國際版《名偵探比卡超》發佈「名偵探比卡超」版Amiibo，這隻比卡超比傳統版比卡超大很多，高達13.6厘米（除去底座和帽子約合13厘米），玩家將這個Amiibo與遊戲聯動還能解鎖獨家視頻，幫助破案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/games/transform/w550h309/20180113/9XTY-fyqrewh5214804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fgames%2Ftransform%2Fw550h309%2F20180113%2F9XTY-fyqrewh5214804.jpg&h=a4cee7e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「事情變得越黎越有趣啦嘿」<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.pokemon.co.jp/ex/meitantei_pikachu/common/images/pikachu/img_05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pokemon.co.jp%2Fex%2Fmeitantei_pikachu%2Fcommon%2Fimages%2Fpikachu%2Fimg_05.jpg&h=b32fab10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n變到好港女既比超卡 會西面 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.pokemon.co.jp/ex/meitantei_pikachu/common/images/pikachu/img_04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pokemon.co.jp%2Fex%2Fmeitantei_pikachu%2Fcommon%2Fimages%2Fpikachu%2Fimg_04.jpg&h=7f85ab8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「唔好命令我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.pokemon.co.jp/ex/meitantei_pikachu/common/images/pikachu/img_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pokemon.co.jp%2Fex%2Fmeitantei_pikachu%2Fcommon%2Fimages%2Fpikachu%2Fimg_02.jpg&h=b9eaa209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網: [url]<a href=\"http://www.pokemon.co.jp/ex/meitantei_pikachu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pokemon.co.jp%2Fex%2Fmeitantei_pikachu%2F&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b65b9f30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.pokemon.co.jp/ex/meitantei_pikachu/</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"30aa0c94d8616ee6979c9de2861bc4a5280211f3","tid":527671,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/ass